ests and their distributions are: semantic (51.34%),\nbuild (15.5%), analysis checks (9.09%), compatibility (7.49%), concurrency\n(4.28%), configuration (4.28%), GUI (2.14%), API (2.14%), security (2.14%), and\nmemory (1.6%).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 May 2022 09:43:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-20"}
